CVS Access
----------
PKP provides anonymous CVS access to the latest Harvester2 code.

CVS web interface: <http://pkp.sfu.ca/cvs/>

Using anonymous CVS:

$ cvs -d :pserver:anonymous@pkp.sfu.ca:/cvs login
(Logging in to anonymous@pkp.sfu.ca)
CVS password: <Enter>
$ cvs -d :pserver:anonymous@pkp.sfu.ca:/cvs co harvester2

Note that you must rename config.TEMPLATE.inc.php to config.inc.php prior to
running the Harvester2 installation script.
